{"tid":1582308,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"Massive Attack多倫多開騷播港警打人片","createTime":"2019-09-20T03:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T11:52:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"42a3595971a0f15b88786270ffa0048e6b659232","tid":1582308,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:58:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190920/20771488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190920%2F20771488&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8g%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=122d999d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190920%2F20771488&h=3100e98d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190920/20771488</a><br />\n<br />\nMassive Attack多倫多開騷播港警打人片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190920/large/1568902170_c972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190920%2Flarge%2F1568902170_c972.jpg&h=7f8712b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMassive Attack主音Robert<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國Trip Hop班霸Massive Attack前晚於加拿大多倫多舉行演唱會，唱到壓軸歌曲《Group four》時，在台上播出香港警方於7月14日在沙田新城市廣場濫捕示威者的片段，以表達對香港人的支持。片段中，共逾10名警察在鏡頭下，仍然毆打手無寸鐵的市民，而《Group four》的歌詞正是關於政府對人民的監控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190920/large/1568902170_6ecb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190920%2Flarge%2F1568902170_6ecb.gif&h=c60c67ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMassive Attack前晚在多倫多開騷，在台上播出香港警方打人的片段。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n其實，Massive Attack一向都很關注香港的政治狀況，他們曾於2017年來港在Clockenflap演出，當時他們亦有在舞台上展示和平佔中的標誌，以及黃之鋒的頭像等支持社運。主音Robert&quot;3D&quot; Del Naja當時接受本報訪問時，就關心本港貧富懸殊與民主的問題，當時他說：「我簡直覺得十分瘋狂，尤其是這處貧富懸殊的狀況，一條橋劃分出兩個不同的世界。我覺得香港的歷史背景讓它成為一個很有趣的地方。首先，曾經作為英國殖民地對於這個地方的影響，我覺得很好奇。我覺得歷史非常重要，而因為殖民的關係，英國變成了歷史重要的部份。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：克己 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【台日合作】李心潔阿部寬壓軸重頭戲"},{"pid":"5f3e866c3383dc5bebd1af68a22715adb8cd56d3","tid":1582308,"uid":132293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F821CnG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF821CnG.jpg&h=623d27fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b406053aa8c0bdc7b89e5b120ec0757afb195b25","tid":1582308,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8g%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=1b17d897\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8g%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=2ec395f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"ce437e0a7a4f6d8146bcea9f004afb5b0dee8ee3","tid":1582308,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:52:50.000Z","msg":"【有啟示】伊館做show 會展奏樂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1596105\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1596105</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}